{"type":"text","timestamp":1784316839054,"sessionID":"ses_08ea082c8ffeulTMP4nVP9BJov","part":{"id":"prt_f719242e00017kIXq3lQEjvt1T","messageID":"msg_f7191b90a001Thcu5Wr4TVN1nw","sessionID":"ses_08ea082c8ffeulTMP4nVP9BJov","type":"text","text":"Five iterations completed and each passed the mechanical artifact check. The final synthesis will preserve the two intentionally unresolved empirical questions, mark the forced `maxIterationsReached` stop, and remain lineage-local.","time":{"start":1784316838624,"end":1784316839053},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0bfc3e07e624f4fb016a5a83a691c48191901954e5c200adb7","phase":"commentary"}}}}
